1. Ab hier Brief von Julie Gundert auf angeklebtem Zettel.
                                                            <4 April 1873>*
611My dear Frederic
.fo +

If you have any thing to be mended bring it when you come please you must
not keep them for your good Emma, The more we see her the more we learn to
value her, God has made you a fine present in her she is daily finer love-
lyer Such gift from God is to be appreciated as from Him who is the giver
of all good gifts.

So we shall soon see you D.V.

                             Adieu my dear Son
.fo -
                                 yours JG.

love from Uranie
